    <div class="main review-item" id="7803664">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7803664/" class="title-link">近距离窥探全球化美军</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7803664"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/taiyunli/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3733291-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/taiyunli/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">远古善良战斗君</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-03-07"
      class="main-meta">2016-03-07 22:05:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7803664_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     《大国威慑》是著名记者和国际政治评论员罗伯特·卡普兰的一部作品。    这本书的作者罗伯特·卡普兰是美国著名的军事记者，在上世纪九十年代的时候，他就以写作巴尔干混乱局势的著作而出名。在此之后，他一直写作各种关于美军和国际政治的通俗著作。这些著作融合了国际政治...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7803664_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7803664_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7728679">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7728679/" class="title-link">中国威胁还是威胁中国！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7728679"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2608758/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2608758-24.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2608758/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">斗樱</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-01-09"
      class="main-meta">2016-01-09 23:12:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7728679_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这两天看的书比较有意思，一本讲了美国的衰落之后必然会带来的中国威胁论，另一本则在无限的夸耀美国的武力强大。前者是为了美国的大选，向反对党开炮；后者大概就是为了更好的迎合美国读者的心理了。基本上作者还是在那抛售“中国威胁论”这老一套，就算没把中国视作是势均力...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7728679_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7728679_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7587204">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7587204/" class="title-link">从一本书中了解大国战争机器的运作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7587204"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
